description:
Dynamo Professional with 7 ACTIONS in 1 WASH, Liquid Laundry Detergent, 1.8L, 36 washloads

Looking for an all-in-one shop? CHOICE RECOMMENDED Dynamo Professional 7 in 1 provides you with 7 Actions in 1 Wash: Its advanced formula with a unqique blend of active ingredients provides you with tough stain removal, thorough deep clean, whitening, brightening, clean & fresh scent, vibrant colours and fabric care - all in one wash! Dynamo Professional - superior results first time! Suitable for front & top loader washing machines. Dynamo Professional tackles even the toughest stains: Oil & grease, grassy stains, mud, tomato-based stains, coffee, cuff & collar grime, perspiration and red wine are no challenge when using Dynamo. Rub a little on the stain and the rest in the wash for best results. Visits Dynamo.com.au for specific stain solutions *Choice recommended 2020

CHOICE recommended Dynamo Professional is the best performing laundry detergent (CHOICE test from Aug'2020)

Advanced 7 in 1 formula to cover all laundry needs for superior results, first time

Provides you with tough stain removal, thorough deep clean, whitening, brightening, clean & fresh scent, vibrant colours and fabric care

Dynamo Professional is the expert against tough stain

Practical designed spout & cap allows easy pouring with without any spillage

Suitable for front & top loader & quick wash cycle
name: Dynamo Professional 7 In 1 Laundry Detergent Liquid 1.8L
